# üöÄ Workshop Hub - Full Stack Final Project

**Workshop Hub** is a robust Full-Stack application designed to manage a workshop catalog. This project serves as the final submission for the React course, demonstrating a deep understanding of component architecture, state management, and secure backend integration.

### Live links
- **üîó Live Demo:** https://workshop-hub-4j2d.onrender.com
- **‚öôÔ∏è Backend API:** https://workshop-hub.onrender.com

